    • コンストラクタの詳細

      • PlayerManager

        public PlayerManager(FlagGameAPI api)
        Create new PlayerManager with new registry. In order to keep consistency, do NOT create new one, use FlagGameAPI.getPlayers().
        パラメータ:
        api - An API instance running on the server to sync this mamager
